Name: UCSB
Description: A great university located along the California Coast!

Name: Leo J. Ryan Park
Description: A great place for walks and boat rides along the Foster City lagoon.

Name: Coyote Point Recreation Area
Description: Beautiful area with lots of trees, a harbor, museums, and a playground for kids.

Name: Muir Woods National Monument
Description: A national park filled with tall redwood trees and good hiking trails.

Name: Hillsdale Shopping Center
Description: A large mall with plenty of different shops and events, as well as a relatively new food court.

Name: Pier 39
Description: A shopping center and a pier that is often visited by people and sea lions alike.
